<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About South Calgary</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">South Calgary’s 50-year development is reflected through the variety of housing styles,
                with lowrise apartments and townhouses, to attached homes and detached bungalow’s and two storey homes.
            </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The area, having a view of downtown and the mountains, also makes it ideal for luxury
                homes. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">In 2001, 61.1% of properties in South Calgary were used for rental purposes, but the
                percentage is likely to have changed.
                South Calgary real estate is known for its proximity to the trendy Marda Loop area. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Situated between the subdivisions of,and, South Calgary homes are well maintained and this
                vibrant neighbourhood is re-creating itself with gorgeous new homes being developed for sale. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">A quick commute to downtown Calgary make homes for sale in South Calgary highly sought
                after.</p>
        </div>
